OL,3,CHow rare was the Channel Islands
OL,4,C'white Christmas'?
OL,6,FA 'white Christmas' was technically
OL,7,Fobserved across the Channel Islands
OL,8,Fthis year.
OL,10,FBut that doesn't mean a blanket of
OL,11,Fsnow.
OL,13,FIf you're wondering why you didn't see
OL,14,Fany flakes, it's because the snow
OL,15,Fflurries fell in the early hours of
OL,16,Fthe morning, between 4am and dawn,
OL,17,Fwhen most of us were asleep.
