OL,3,CHow rare was the Channel Islands
OL,4,C'white Christmas'?
OL,6,FThe white stuff fell in both Guernsey
OL,7,Fand Jersey, but there wasn't much of
OL,8,Fit - too few flakes to cover the
OL,9,Fground or stick around.
OL,11,FWhat is the definition of a 'white
OL,12,FChristmas'?
OL,14,FMeteorologically speaking, only one
OL,15,Fsnowflake is required to fall for it
OL,16,Fto count as a 'white Christmas' - as
OL,17,Flong as this is recorded officially by
OL,18,FJersey or Guernsey Met.
