OL,3,CHow rare was the Channel Islands
OL,4,C'white Christmas'?
OL,6,FThat is why 2025 was technically a
OL,7,F'white Christmas' for the Channel
OL,8,FIslands, despite us not seeing deep
OL,9,Fflurries of snow.
OL,11,FWhen did it last snow on Christmas Day
OL,12,Fin the Channel Islands?
OL,14,F1970 was the last official 'white
OL,15,FChristmas' - with flakes in both
OL,16,FGuernsey and Jersey - but as in 2025,
OL,17,Fit didn't settle.
