OL,3,CHow rare was the Channel Islands
OL,4,C'white Christmas'?
OL,6,FWhy do we picture Christmas as a snowy
OL,7,Ftime?
OL,9,FOur Christmas cards feature snow-
OL,10,Fcapped villages and flurries of flakes
OL,11,Fare a common feature in Christmas
OL,12,Fmusic.
OL,14,FBut Christmas isn't a particularly
OL,15,Fsnowy month - statistically speaking,
OL,16,Fyou are more likely to see snow around
OL,17,FEaster than you are at Christmas.
