OL,3,CHow rare was the Channel Islands
OL,4,C'white Christmas'?
OL,6,FOn average, December sees around 4mm
OL,7,Fof rain daily, making it the rainiest
OL,8,Fmonth of the year.
OL,10,FOther big snow events
OL,12,FWe have seen the odd significant
OL,13,Fsnowfall event over the years.
OL,15,FThe most recent blanketing was in
OL,16,FJanuary 2024, when between 2cm and 5cm
OL,17,Ffell across the islands, with flights
OL,18,Fgrounded.
